locality: Dzombo. Hill 120-470m, igneous intrusion with moist semi-deciduous forest. Dominants:Scorodophloeos,Cola clavata,C.minor,Ricinodendron,Combretum schumannii,CraibiaManilkara,Haplocoelopsis,Drypetes. Lianes: Combretum,Salacia,Dichapetalum.
Kwemchungwa Forest under supervision of Msimamo Group, S of Mpangamanyoka Village forest of Kiwanda near Mlinga Forest Reserve.
Pangani. Upriver. Remnant forest along rocky river & on hill slope w Julbernardia,Brachystegia Manilkara sansibarensis, Cola porphyrantha.
Lokutu. Unilever palm oil plantation. Pt 647 Lukumete Forest Camp.

Kwale Distr. Shimba Hills. Kivumoni. Lowland forest on red soil with Erythrophleum, Paramacrolobium, Croton sylvaticus, Xylopia, Pachystela brevipes & Diospyros shimbaensis, D. greenwayi, Tricalysia microphylla under.
Shimba Hills. Mkongani West. Lowland forest much destroyed by elephant w Combretum schumannii, Drypetes, Scorodophloeus, Julbernardia, Pachystela & Hyphaene grassland outside
Ngarama North Forest Reserve; pt 455, dry coastal forest.
